<p>The social network allowed advertisers to buy ads specifically targeting "Jew haters" and people who were "interested in" other anti-Semitic topics, according to a <a href="https://www.propublica.org/article/facebook-enabled-advertisers-to-reach-jew-haters">new report</a> from <em>ProPublica</em>.</p>
