<p>Archive lets you hide photos and videos from your profile without completely deleting them. That way, you can bring them back later if you want to do so.&#160;</p>
<div><p>SEE ALSO: <a href="http://mashable.com/2017/08/08/apple-instagram-needs-help/">Apple&#8217;s Instagram account reeks of desperation</a></p></div>
<p>Instagram <a href="https://instagram-press.com/blog/2017/06/13/archive/">phrases it</a> as giving you the flexibility to represent how you evolve over time, but Archive is really just a way to hide embarrassing selfies or videos that didn't get enough likes. Because we've all seen the classic "felt cute, might delete later" post.&#160;</p>
