<p>On Instagram, Kendall Jenner, Emily Ratajkowski, Bella Hadid, and other models once encouraged people to attend Fyre Festival. Yeah, we're talking about the music event that ended up featuring <a href="http://mashable.com/2017/09/01/fyre-fest-bankruptcy/">no music</a> and landing itself <a href="http://mashable.com/2017/05/10/fyre-fest-lawsuit-best-lines/">seven fraud and class action lawsuits</a>.&#160;</p>
